quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,222,"Hi…ďe naam-no maa fii fiilordu, maaku: ∆äum ko nefinii …óum; luncitee rew…ďe …ďen fewndo fiilordu, wata on …ďa…óto …ďe haa …ďe laa…ďa. Si …ďe laa…ďii, ngaree e ma…ď…ďe nokku ka Alla Yamiri on …óon. Pellet Alla No Yi…ói tuubaya…ďe …ďen Himo Yi…ói kadi …ďen la…ď…ďinotoo…ďe"
  2,223,"Rew…ďe mon …ďen ko gese mo'on. Ngardee e ngesa mon mbam nokku kala ka faalira…óon, ngardinanee woŇčkiiji mon …óin. Hulle Alla, nganndon ko on kawroo…ďe e Makko. Weltin gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  2,224,"Wata on wa…óu Alla heedo fii ngoondooje mon …óen; nde …óiggoton, gom…óon hulon mo∆ī∆īinon hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,225,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on gardambi=bolle mehre ka ngoondooje mo'on, kono Himo Nanngitira on kon ko …ďer…óe mon …óen faggitii. Alla ko Hafroowo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  2,226,"No woodani …ďen woondiroo…ďe suddii…ďe mun …ďen: habbitagol lebbi nayi. Si …ďe ruttike, pellet Alla ko Haforoowo Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,227,"Si …ďe fellitii ceergal ngal, pellet Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,228,"Seeraa…ďe …ďen yo habbiŇčtin ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen laa…ďe tati; dagaŇčtaako …ďe suu…óugol kon ko Alla Tagi ka ndeer renngaaji ma…ď…ďe, si wonii hi…ďe gom…óim…ďe Alla e √Īalaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe jojjidi ruttugol …ďe e …óum, si hawrii hi…ďe faalaa weldital. No woodani …ďen [rew…ďe] yeru kon ko fawii…ďe, no mo∆ī∆īiri. No woodani wor…ďe …ďen: …ďural e dow ma…ď…ďe. Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"